videos.headline: McKoy breaks loose for a 33-yard score
videos.description: Kennedy McKoy goes 33-yards to the house to give West Virginia a 10-3 lead over TCU.

videos.headline: TCU fumble sets Mountaineers up with good field position
videos.description: TCU's Kennedy Reed fumbles on a kick return and Exree Loe recovers for West Virginia on TCU's 17-yard line.

videos.headline: West Virginia punches in one-yard score
videos.description: Martell Pettaway runs it up the middle for a one-yard touchdown to give West Virginia a 17-3 lead over TCU.

videos.headline: Grier finds wide-open TE for score
videos.description: Will Grier connects with his tight end Trevon Wesco for a 32-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: West Virginia opens up lead over TCU
videos.description: Kennedy McKoy rushes for his second touchdown of the day to give West Virginia a 33-3 lead over TCU.

videos.headline: Reagor hooks up with WR for catch in end zone
videos.description: Jalen Reagor finds his receiver Michael Collins in the end zone with a defender right in his face.

videos.headline: Grier throws 8-yard score
videos.description: West Virginia takes advantage of the red zone opportunity with an 8-yard score.
